{"tid":1874041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柒婆根本是超級典型臭閪老母姓格","createTime":"2020-02-11T03:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-11T04:04:12.000Z","uid":81783,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"46859496dfd8435f76e7364b00f57b42168c47fa","tid":1874041,"uid":81783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:37:13.000Z","msg":"依條死臭閪柒婆，根本同「典型臭閪老母」完全無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你越叫佢做果樣野，佢就死都唔撚做<br />\n你越叫佢唔好做果樣野，佢就拿拿聲去做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等同叫老母而家唔好去酒樓飲茶，好多病菌呀，佢就死都要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n掉番轉你同老母講你快去飲茶啦，好想你快d死呀，以後唔洗對住你呀，個老母自然就唔會去飲茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n簡單講，即係死唔撚認輸，死都要鬥贏<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以而家應該搞一次遊行叫林鄭「通關」，一齊好開心大叫好想快d死，好想快d去天堂，我地要一齊早一步比林鄭上天堂呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"d91504348f975f581c533755dc9351514d268984","tid":1874041,"uid":346806,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:39:37.000Z","msg":"咁睇我媽都幾好，至少我屌完佢肯聽肯做"},{"pid":"59ed70600378bcdf4447faa8bc3add33ad8ff8a4","tid":1874041,"uid":81783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d91504348f975f581c533755dc9351514d268984","tid":1874041,"uid":346806,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:39:37.000Z","msg":"咁睇我媽都幾好，至少我屌完佢肯聽肯做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T03:41:01.000Z","msg":"幸福寶寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01b5f4f25e7a6f71d86a887cccb24442e88d4de","tid":1874041,"uid":50196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi